frames.caption: A young woman sits on a littered street, surrounded by bags of trash. She is focused on eating from a small container, seemingly oblivious to her surroundings.
frames.description: The scene depicts an urban setting with a desolate atmosphere. The street is lined with garbage bags, and the buildings appear worn and neglected, suggesting a rundown area.
